### ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### Tests appointment-service (Spring Boot)
### Port : 8082
### Variables : ouvre View > Tool Windows > Services > HTTP Client
### ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

@host = http://localhost:8082
@token = REMPLACE_PAR_LE_TOKEN_RECU_AU_LOGIN

### ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### 1. AUTHENTIFICATION
### ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### 1.1 — Inscrire un patient
POST {{host}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Douae Test",
  "email": "douae.test@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "phone": "0612345678"
}

### 1.2 — Login (récupère le token)
POST {{host}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "douae.test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 1.3 — Créer un staff (Doctor) — nécessite être Secretary
POST {{host}}/api/auth/staff
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Dr Ahmed Bennani",
  "email": "dr.bennani@hospital.com",
  "password": "doctor123",
  "phone": "0700000001",
  "role": "Doctor"
}

### ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### 2. SERVICES (spécialités hospitalières)
### ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### 2.1 — Lister les services (public)
GET {{host}}/api/services

### 2.2 — Créer un service (Secretary)
POST {{host}}/api/services
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Cardiologie",
  "description": "Service de cardiologie",
  "icon": "heart"
}

### 2.3 — Lister les médecins d'un service
GET {{host}}/api/services/1/doctors

### 2.4 — Affecter des services à un médecin (Secretary)
POST {{host}}/api/services/assign
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "doctorId": 2,
  "serviceIds": [1, 2]
}

### ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### 3. CRÉNEAUX (Slots)
### ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### 3.1 — Créer un créneau unique (Doctor)
POST {{host}}/api/slots
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "startTime": "2026-05-04T09:00:00",
  "endTime": "2026-05-04T09:30:00"
}

### 3.2 — Créer une semaine de créneaux en masse (Doctor)
POST {{host}}/api/slots/bulk
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "weekStartDate": "2026-05-04",
  "slotStartTime": "09:00:00",
  "slotEndTime": "17:00:00",
  "slotDurationMinutes": 30,
  "workDays": ["MONDAY", "TUESDAY", "WEDNESDAY", "THURSDAY", "FRIDAY"]
}

### 3.3 — Voir les créneaux d'un médecin pour une semaine (public)
GET {{host}}/api/slots/doctor/2/week?weekStart=2026-05-04

### 3.4 — Vérifier si la semaine est complète
GET {{host}}/api/slots/doctor/2/week-full?weekStart=2026-05-04

### 3.5 — Bloquer un créneau (Doctor)
PATCH {{host}}/api/slots/1/block
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3.6 — Débloquer un créneau (Doctor)
PATCH {{host}}/api/slots/1/unblock
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3.7 — Créneaux hospitaliers (DoctorId=NULL, ex. Radiologie)
GET {{host}}/api/slots/hospital/3/week?weekStart=2026-05-04

### ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### 4. RENDEZ-VOUS (Appointments)
### ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### 4.1 — Réserver en tant que patient connecté
POST {{host}}/api/appointments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "timeSlotId": 1,
  "reason": "Consultation de routine"
}

### 4.2 — Réserver en anonyme (récupère un anonymousToken !)
POST {{host}}/api/appointments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "timeSlotId": 2,
  "reason": "Première consultation",
  "patientName": "Patient Anonyme",
  "patientEmail": "anonyme@example.com",
  "patientPhone": "0699999999"
}

### 4.3 — Voir mes rendez-vous
GET {{host}}/api/appointments/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4.4 — Détail d'un rendez-vous
GET {{host}}/api/appointments/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4.5 — Replanifier un rendez-vous
PUT {{host}}/api/appointments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "appointmentId": 1,
  "newTimeSlotId": 5,
  "reason": "Changement d'horaire"
}

### 4.6 — Annuler en tant que patient connecté
DELETE {{host}}/api/appointments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "appointmentId": 1,
  "cancelReason": "Empêchement"
}

### 4.7 — Annuler en anonyme (avec token reçu lors de la réservation)
DELETE {{host}}/api/appointments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "appointmentId": 2,
  "cancelReason": "Empêchement",
  "anonymousToken": "REMPLACE_PAR_LE_TOKEN_RECU"
}

### ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### 5. LISTE D'ATTENTE
### ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### 5.1 — S'inscrire sur la liste d'attente d'un médecin
POST {{host}}/api/waiting-list
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "doctorId": 2,
  "weekStartDate": "2026-05-04",
  "patientName": "Marie Dupont",
  "email": "marie@example.com",
  "phone": "0611111111"
}

### 5.2 — Lister les inscrits chez un médecin pour une semaine
GET {{host}}/api/waiting-list/doctor/2?weekStart=2026-05-04

### 5.3 — Se désinscrire
DELETE {{host}}/api/waiting-list/1?email=marie@example.com

### ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### 6. INTERNAL BRIDGE (pour ms-patient-personnel et chatbot)
### ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### 6.1 — Health check
GET {{host}}/api/internal/health

### 6.2 — Rendez-vous d'un patient par email
GET {{host}}/api/internal/patient/douae.test@example.com/appointments

### 6.3 — Créneaux disponibles d'un médecin sur une période
GET {{host}}/api/internal/doctor/2/available-slots?startDate=2026-05-04&endDate=2026-05-10

### 6.4 — Détail d'un RDV par id+email
GET {{host}}/api/internal/appointment/1?email=douae.test@example.com
